cs.CY, cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL

This paper deals with the enforcement of the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) and uses machine learning techniques for regression analysis. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of Cybersecurity (cs.CR), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), and Computational Linguistics (cs.CL). Additionally, since the paper deals with legal aspects of data protection, it could also belong to the category of Computers and Society (cs.CY).
